Enable CRM Analytics for Experience Cloud Sites

Securely share CRM Analytics apps with an Experience Cloud site partner and customer users.

To enable CRM Analytics for sharing in Experience Cloud sites, complete these steps:

1. From Setup, enter Analytics in the Quick Find box, then select Settings.
2. Select Share Analytics with Communities.
3. In Setup, assign your community members the CRM Analytics for Communities permission set license.
4. Create a permission set that includes the View CRM Analytics on Experience Cloud pages permission and assign it to your community members.
